Class AbstractStringDomain

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.openapi.resolver.AbstractValueDomain<T>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueDomain<String>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AsciiStringDomain, EmailDomain, MediaTypeDomain, PropertyNameDomain, TimeDomain, UuidDomain

    public abstract class AbstractStringDomain
extends SequenceDomain<String>
    Defines a set of string values that can be used by a request.
